ntrol systems</li>\n	<li>motors and alternators</li>\n	<li>cabling / installation</li>\n	<li>project management</li>\n	<li>harmonics and FMEA analyses</li>\n</ul>\nThis makes it possible to offer conventional as well as innovative solutions to provide power for industry/government. This leads to effective operational management and production based on continuity.[/fusion_text][/one_half][one_half last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][imageframe lightbox=\"no\" lightbox_image=\"\" style_type=\"none\" bordercolor=\"\" bordersize=\"0px\" borderradius=\"0\" stylecolor=\"\" align=\"center\" link=\"\" linktarget=\"_self\" animation_type=\"bounce\" animation_direction=\"down\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"] <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/bem/wp-content/uploads/bem-power-startseite-01-300x296.png\" />[/imageframe][/one_half][/fullwidth]\";s:9:\"Über Uns\";s:1448:\"[one_full last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]\n<h1>Über uns</h1>\n<h2>Electrical machines up to 30 000kVA <strong>         </strong></h2>\nBayerische Elektrische Maschinen manufactures premium quality motors and alternators from 500kVA to 30 000kVA under the BEM® product brands\n\nWe use our experience and knowledge gathered from a large and diverse number of applications of motor and generator installations worldwide to provide expertise in offering integrated design solutions that help our customers compete more successfully throughout the world\n\nInternationally renowned for built-in quality, our machines set the standard for ruggedness, reliability and versatility.\n<h3><strong>Our Mission</strong></h3>\nOur mission is to aid the sustainable growth of our customer’s businesses globally.\n\nWe provide individual innovative solutions inspired by relentless efforts to understand our customer’s needs and their specific applications.\n\nWe leverage our extensive knowledge, product performance and service to increase the competitiveness, efficiency and productivity of our partners globally.[/fusion_text][/one_full]\";s:8:\"Produkte\";s:4645:\"[one_full last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][imageframe lightbox=\"no\" lightbox_image=\"\" style_type=\"none\" bordercolor=\"\" bordersize=\"0px\" borderradius=\"0\" stylecolor=\"\" align=\"center\" link=\"\" linktarget=\"_self\" animation_type=\"0\" animation_direction=\"down\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"] <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/bem/wp-content/uploads/produkt-logo-bem-300x146.jpg\" />[/imageframe][/one_full][one_half last=\"no\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]\n<h2>BEML - Series</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>Low voltage motor/alternator</li>\n	<li>Voltage: 400V, 480V, 690V</li>\n	<li>Power: 600 – 6,000kVA</li>\n	<li>Speed: 500 – 1800 rpm</li>\n	<li>4 to 12 pole</li>\n	<li>50 /60 Hz</li>\n</ul>\n[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\n<h3>Product Range</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-132\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/bem/wp-content/uploads/bem-produktbilder-02.png\" alt=\"bem-produktbilder-02\" width=\"640\" height=\"204\" />\n<ul>\n	<li>Low voltage motor/generator</li>\n	<li>Voltage: 400V, 480V, 690V</li>\n	<li>Power: 600 – 6,000kVA</li>\n	<li>Speed: 500 – 1800 rpm</li>\n	<li>4 to 12 pole</li>\n	<li>50 /60 Hz</li>\n</ul>\n[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\n<h3>Standards</h3>\nBEM products are designed according to the following standards：\n<ul>\n	<li>IEC / EN 60034</li>\n	<li>BS5000</li>\n	<li>VDE 0530</li>\n	<li>ISO8528-9</li>\n	<li>Ship classification society: ABS / BV / CCS / DNV</li>\n	<li>On customer request: UL / CSA / NEMA</li>\n</ul>\n[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\n<h3>Protection</h3>\nProduct feature as standard open drip-proof enclosure in accordance with IP23/IC01\n\nAlternative cooling and enclosure options:\n<h4>Enclosure features (IEC60034-5)</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>IP43 - filters fitted</li>\n	<li>IP44/IP54 - totally enclosed air/air or air/water heat exchangers with leakage detection</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Cooling features (IEC60034-6)</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>IC11 - air inlet ducted</li>\n	<li>IC21 - air outlet ducted</li>\n	<li>IC31 - inlet and outlet ducted</li>\n	<li>IC616/611 - air/air heat exchanger</li>\n	<li>IC81W - air/water heat exchanger with leakage detection</li>\n</ul>\n[/fusion_text][/one_half][one_half last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]\n<h2>BEMH - Series</h2>\n<ul>\n	<li>High voltage motor/alternator</li>\n	<li>Voltage: 3.3 – 15kV</li>\n	<li>Power: 0.5 – 30MVA</li>\n	<li>Speed: 500 – 1800rpm</li>\n	<li>4 to 14 pole</li>\n	<li>50 /60 Hz</li>\n</ul>\n[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\n<h3>Product Range</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-133\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1/bem/wp-content/uploads/bem-produktbilder-01.png\" alt=\"bem-produktbilder-01\" width=\"640\" height=\"204\" />\n<ul>\n	<li>High voltage motor/generator</li>\n	<li>Voltage: 3.3 – 15kV</li>\n	<li>Power: 0.5 – 30MVA</li>\n	<li>Speed: 500 – 1800rpm</li>\n	<li>4 to 14 pole</li>\n	<li>50 /60 Hz</li>\n</ul>\n[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\n<h3>Standards</h3>\nBEM products are designed according to the following standards：\n<ul>\n	<li>IEC / EN 60034</li>\n	<li>BS5000</li>\n	<li>VDE 0530</li>\n	<li>ISO8528-9</li>\n	<li>Ship classification society: ABS / BV / CCS / DNV</li>\n	<li>On customer request: UL / CSA / NEMA</li>\n</ul>\n[/fusion_text][fusion_text]\n<h3>Protection</h3>\nProduct feature as standard open drip-proof enclosure in accordance with IP23/IC01\n\nAlternative cooling and enclosure options:\n<h4>Enclosure features (IEC60034-5)</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>IP43 - filters fitted</li>\n	<li>IP44/IP54 - totally enclosed air/air or air/water heat exchangers with leakage detection</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Cooling features (IEC60034-6)</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>IC11 - air inlet ducted</li>\n	<li>IC21 - air outlet ducted</li>\n	<li>IC31 - inlet and outlet ducted</li>\n	<li>IC616/611 - air/air heat exchanger</li>\n	<li>IC81W - air/water heat exchanger with leakage detection</li>\n</ul>\n[/fusion_text][/one_half]\";s:11:\"anwendungen\";s:9802:\"[fullwidth background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_parallax=\"none\" enable_mobile=\"no\" parallax_speed=\"0.3\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" video_url=\"\" video_aspect_ratio=\"16:9\" video_webm=\"\" video_mp4=\"\" video_ogv=\"\" video_preview_image=\"\" overlay_co