7/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-150x42.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1.png 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible themes.</p>\n<p>The themes are: <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/panarea-restaurant-and-food-wordpress-theme/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Panarea</a>, <a href=\"https://weblizar.com/themes/fashionair-premium/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fashionair</a>, <a href=\"https://www.proteusthemes.com/wordpress-themes/buildpress/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">BuildPress</a>, <a href=\"https://leadinjection.io/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Leadinjection</a>, <a href=\"http://themegrill.com/themes/ample/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">AmplePro</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if youâ€™re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with ourÂ <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Panarea</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce compatible theme with many options especially focused on restaurants and food in general.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/wordpress/panarea-restaurant-and-food-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Panarea</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Fashionair</h2>\n<blockquote><p>WooCommerce WordPress theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://weblizar.com/themes/fashionair-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Fashionair</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">BuildPress</h2>\n<blockquote><p>BuildPress is customizable WordPress theme suitable for construction and building business.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.proteusthemes.com/wordpress-themes/buildpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase BuildPress</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Leadinjection</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Leadinjection is a WordPress landing page theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://leadinjection.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Leadinjection</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">AmplePro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Multipurpose Responsive WordPress Theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://themegrill.com/themes/ample/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase AmplePro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=mhhKOkZPS0c:cob8_jLG_8c:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=mhhKOkZPS0c:cob8_jLG_8c:D7Dq