al program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with ourÂ <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Post Type Builder</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Post Type Builder is an &#8220;all-in-one&#8221; WordPress plugin for creating custom post types, taxonomies, and post type templates.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themify.me/post-type-builder\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Post Type Builder</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Convert Pro</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Convert Pro is an advanced lead generation popup plugin with a drag and drop editor that helps you create beautiful popups and opt-in forms to boost your website conversions.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.convertplug.com/pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Convert Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Events Schedule</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Events WordPress plugin</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://codecanyon.net/item/events-schedule-wordpress-plugin/14907462\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase Events Schedule</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Tour Operator</h2>\n<blockquote><p>LightSpeedâ€™s LSX Tour Operator plugin is here to help you take your Tour Operator business online.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress