;s:27:\"https://wpml.org/?p=1517107\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:381:\"OceanWP is a free lightweight multipurpose WordPress theme. The theme is highly customizable and easy-to-use. It provides many pre-built demos and compatible with page builders like, Elementor, Beaver Builder, Divi Builder, and WPBakery page builder which are all WPML compatible. In cooperation with OceanWP team, we managed to make OceanWP compatible with WPML. We have [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Mohamed Khafaja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2714:\"<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1517113 size-full\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/OceanWP-compatibility-with-WPML.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"509\" srcset=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/OceanWP-compatibility-with-WPML.png 1200w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/OceanWP-compatibility-with-WPML-150x64.png 150w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/OceanWP-compatibility-with-WPML-300x127.png 300w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/OceanWP-compatibility-with-WPML-768x326.png 768w, https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/OceanWP-compatibility-with-WPML-1024x434.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://oceanwp.org/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">OceanWP</a> is a free lightweight multipurpose WordPress theme. The theme is highly customizable and easy-to-use. It provides many pre-built demos and compatible with page builders like, Elementor, Beaver Builder, Divi Builder, and WPBakery page builder which are all WPML compatible.</p>\n<p>In cooperation with OceanWP team, we managed to make OceanWP compatible with WPML. We have prepared a tutorial that explains <a href=\"https://goo.gl/5QMtT8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the process of building multilingual sites using OceanWP and WPML</a>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1517117\" src=\"https://cdn.wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/OceanWP-compatibility-with-WPML-in-action.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1698\" height=\"882\" /></p>\n<p>OceanWP offers premium extensions that allow you to even further customize your website with ease. We made sure that these extensions work flawlessly with WPML. This is a guide that explains <a href=\"https://goo.gl/Y2C8xK\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">translating the textual elements generated by these extensions</a>.</p>\n<p>Are you already using OceanWP theme along with WPML to build multilingual websites? Share your experience with us in the comments section below.</p>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=tAEFA9A84CU:05P8hd19n88:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=tAEFA9A84CU:05P8hd19n88:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=tAEFA9A84CU:05P8hd19n88:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=tAEFA9A84CU:05P8hd19n88:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=tAEFA9A84CU:05P8hd19n88:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=tAEFA9A84CU:05P8hd19n88:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/tAEFA9A84CU\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformed